&lt;p&gt;This role is focused on product thinking, decision-making, and execution in a fast-moving startup environment. We are looking for someone who thrives in ambiguity, collaborates closely with product and engineering, and can take ownership of complex problems from concept through launch.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
